  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, am I going to jail?",
      "zh": "等等，我要被關進監獄嗎？",
      "ja": "待って、私、刑務所に行くの？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Stand on one foot, count slowly.",
      "zh": "單腳站立，慢慢數數。",
      "ja": "片足で立って、ゆっくり数えて。",
      "time": "00:00:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One, two, three.",
      "zh": "一、二、三。",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You want to know how I got here?",
      "zh": "你想知道我是怎麼來到這裡的嗎？",
      "ja": "どうやってここに来たか知りたい？",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good morning. Today is day two in the U.S.",
      "zh": "早安。今天是我在美國的第二天。",
      "ja": "おはよう。今日はアメリカでの2日目だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am traveling alone.",
      "zh": "我一個人旅行。",
      "ja": "一人で旅行している。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And now I'm very hungry.",
      "zh": "現在我很餓。",
      "ja": "そして今、とてもお腹が空いている。",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's eat donuts.",
      "zh": "我們來吃甜甜圈吧。",
      "ja": "ドーナツを食べよう。",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They are very popular in America.",
      "zh": "它們在美國非常受歡迎。",
      "ja": "アメリカではとても人気があるよ。",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning. What would you like?",
      "zh": "早安。你想要什麼？",
      "ja": "おはようございます。何にしますか？",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi. I want a donut.",
      "zh": "嗨。我想要一個甜甜圈。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。ドーナツを一つください。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just one donut?",
      "zh": "只有一個甜甜圈嗎？",
      "ja": "ドーナツは一つだけですか？",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Or do you want six or twelve?",
      "zh": "還是你要六個或十二個？",
      "ja": "それとも6個か12個にしますか？",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Twelve?",
      "zh": "十二個？",
      "ja": "12個？",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is twelve?",
      "zh": "十二是什麼？",
      "ja": "12って何？",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Twelve donuts is one dozen.",
      "zh": "十二個甜甜圈是一打。",
      "ja": "ドーナツ12個は1ダースです。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Six donuts is half a dozen.",
      "zh": "六個甜甜圈是半打。",
      "ja": "ドーナツ6個は半ダースです。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I see.",
      "zh": "喔，我懂了。",
      "ja": "ああ、わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How much is one dozen?",
      "zh": "一打多少錢？",
      "ja": "1ダースはいくらですか？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One dozen is eleven ninety-nine.",
      "zh": "一打是11.99美元。",
      "ja": "1ダースは11ドル99セントです。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One donut is one twenty-five.",
      "zh": "一個甜甜圈是1.25美元。",
      "ja": "ドーナツ1個は1ドル25セントです。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If I buy twelve, can I choose different flavors?",
      "zh": "如果我買十二個，可以選不同口味嗎？",
      "ja": "12個買うと、違う味を選べますか？",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, of course. You can choose many flavors.",
      "zh": "當然可以。你可以選很多口味。",
      "ja": "はい、もちろんです。いろんな味を選べますよ。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good. I like many colors.",
      "zh": "好。我喜歡多種顏色。",
      "ja": "いいね。色んな色が好き。",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want different flavors.",
      "zh": "我想要不同口味。",
      "ja": "違う味が欲しいです。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay. What flavors do you want?",
      "zh": "好的。你想要什麼口味？",
      "ja": "わかりました。どの味にしますか？",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Two chocolate please.",
      "zh": "請給我兩個巧克力口味。",
      "ja": "チョコレートを2つください。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Two pink. Two with sugar on top.",
      "zh": "兩個粉紅色的。兩個上面有糖的。",
      "ja": "ピンクのを2つ。砂糖がかかったのを2つ。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You mean glazed donuts?",
      "zh": "你是說糖霜甜甜圈嗎？",
      "ja": "グレーズドーナツのこと？",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, the shiny ones and one of each other flavor.",
      "zh": "是的，就是那種有光澤的，其他口味各一個。",
      "ja": "はい、光っているやつと他の味をそれぞれ1つずつ。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great. Here you are.",
      "zh": "太好了。給你。",
      "ja": "いいですね。どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Enjoy your donuts.",
      "zh": "請慢用你的甜甜圈。",
      "ja": "ドーナツを楽しんでください。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you. Have a nice day.",
      "zh": "謝謝。祝你有美好的一天。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。良い一日を。",
      "time": "00:01:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "さようなら。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow. Twelve donuts.",
      "zh": "哇，十二個甜甜圈。",
      "ja": "わあ、ドーナツ12個も。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That is a lot of food.",
      "zh": "那真是很多食物。",
      "ja": "それはたくさんの食べ物だね。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am joking.",
      "zh": "我開玩笑的。",
      "ja": "冗談だよ。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I still want a big steak tonight.",
      "zh": "但我今晚還是想吃大牛排。",
      "ja": "でも今夜は大きなステーキが食べたい。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need to call the restaurant to book a table.",
      "zh": "我需要打電話給餐廳訂位。",
      "ja": "レストランに電話して予約しなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello, Golden Steakhouse.",
      "zh": "你好，黃金牛排館。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、ゴールデンステーキハウスです。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How can I help you?",
      "zh": "我能為你做什麼？",
      "ja": "ご用件は何でしょうか？",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi. I want to book a table.",
      "zh": "嗨。我想訂一個位子。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。テーブルを予約したいです。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "For one person.",
      "zh": "一個人。",
      "ja": "一人分です。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "At seven tonight.",
      "zh": "今晚七點。",
      "ja": "今夜7時に。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me check.",
      "zh": "讓我查一下。",
      "ja": "確認しますね。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One moment please.",
      "zh": "請稍等。",
      "ja": "少々お待ちください。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "申し訳ありません。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Seven is full tonight.",
      "zh": "今晚七點已滿。",
      "ja": "今夜7時は満席です。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want another time?",
      "zh": "你想要其他時間嗎？",
      "ja": "他の時間はいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Seven is the only time.",
      "zh": "七點是唯一的時間。",
      "ja": "7時しか無理です。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is there any table at seven?",
      "zh": "七點有空位嗎？",
      "ja": "7時に空いているテーブルはありますか？",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me check again.",
      "zh": "讓我再查一次。",
      "ja": "もう一度確認します。",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, we have one table at 645.",
      "zh": "喔，我們在6:45有一桌。",
      "ja": "ああ、6時45分に1テーブル空いています。",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is that okay?",
      "zh": "可以嗎？",
      "ja": "それでよろしいですか？",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "645 is good.",
      "zh": "6:45很好。",
      "ja": "6時45分でいいです。",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great. What is your name?",
      "zh": "太好了。你的名字是？",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。お名前は？",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My name is Maya.",
      "zh": "我叫瑪雅。",
      "ja": "私の名前はマヤです。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "M-A-Y-A.",
      "zh": "M-A-Y-A。",
      "ja": "M-A-Y-Aです。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your table is booked for 645.",
      "zh": "你的桌位已訂在6:45。",
      "ja": "6時45分に予約が取れました。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you very much.",
      "zh": "非常感謝。",
      "ja": "どうもありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See you later.",
      "zh": "待會見。",
      "ja": "また後で。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you tonight.",
      "zh": "今晚見。",
      "ja": "今夜お会いしましょう。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is still morning.",
      "zh": "現在還是早上。",
      "ja": "まだ朝です。",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The restaurant is in the city center.",
      "zh": "餐廳在市中心。",
      "ja": "レストランは市の中心にあります。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want to go there early.",
      "zh": "我想早點去那裡。",
      "ja": "早めに行きたい。",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The city center has many shops.",
      "zh": "市中心有很多商店。",
      "ja": "市の中心にはたくさんの店があります。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I can buy some new shoes.",
      "zh": "也許我可以買雙新鞋。",
      "ja": "新しい靴を買えるかも。",
      "time": "00:02:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will call an Uber now.",
      "zh": "我現在要叫Uber。",
      "ja": "今、ウーバーを呼びます。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is Mike.",
      "zh": "我是Mike。",
      "ja": "マイクです。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am your driver.",
      "zh": "我是你的司機。",
      "ja": "あなたのドライバーです。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am two minutes away.",
      "zh": "我兩分鐘後到。",
      "ja": "あと2分で着きます。",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi, Mike.",
      "zh": "嗨，Mike。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、マイク。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is Maya.",
      "zh": "我是瑪雅。",
      "ja": "マヤです。",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am at the hotel door.",
      "zh": "我在飯店門口。",
      "ja": "ホテルの入口にいます。",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, sorry.",
      "zh": "喔，抱歉。",
      "ja": "あ、ごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am not at the door.",
      "zh": "我不在門口。",
      "ja": "入口にはいません。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am on the street corner.",
      "zh": "我在街角。",
      "ja": "通りの角にいます。",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you near a streetlight?",
      "zh": "你在路燈附近嗎？",
      "ja": "街灯の近くですか？",
      "time": "00:03:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am wearing a brown coat.",
      "zh": "我穿著棕色外套。",
      "ja": "茶色のコートを着ています。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can see me.",
      "zh": "你可以看到我。",
      "ja": "見えるはずです。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have one suitcase.",
      "zh": "我有一個行李箱。",
      "ja": "スーツケースが一つあります。",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is there space in your car?",
      "zh": "你的車有空位嗎？",
      "ja": "車にスペースはありますか？",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "有的。",
      "ja": "はい、あります。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There is space.",
      "zh": "有空位。",
      "ja": "スペースがあります。",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is the road busy?",
      "zh": "路上擁擠嗎？",
      "ja": "道路は混んでいますか？",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am here now.",
      "zh": "我現在到了。",
      "ja": "今、着きました。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "zh": "我們走吧。",
      "ja": "行きましょう。",
      "time": "00:03:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How can I help you?",
      "zh": "我能幫你什麼？",
      "ja": "何かお手伝いできますか？",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like these shoes.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這雙鞋。",
      "ja": "この靴が好きです。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you have other colors?",
      "zh": "你們有其他顏色嗎？",
      "ja": "他の色はありますか？",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "すみません。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We only have this color.",
      "zh": "我們只有這個顏色。",
      "ja": "この色だけです。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I try these in size 8?",
      "zh": "我可以試穿8號嗎？",
      "ja": "サイズ8を試着できますか？",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Size 8?",
      "zh": "8號？",
      "ja": "サイズ8ですか？",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, please.",
      "zh": "是的，請給我。",
      "ja": "はい、お願いします。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here you go.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do they feel?",
      "zh": "穿起來怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "履き心地はどうですか？",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They are a little big.",
      "zh": "有點大。",
      "ja": "ちょっと大きいです。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you have size 7 and a half?",
      "zh": "你們有7號半嗎？",
      "ja": "7とハーフはありますか？",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me check.",
      "zh": "讓我查一下。",
      "ja": "確認しますね。",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here is size 7 and a half.",
      "zh": "這是7號半。",
      "ja": "こちらが7とハーフです。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, these are perfect.",
      "zh": "喔，這雙很合適。",
      "ja": "ああ、これがぴったりです。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can I also see those shoes over there?",
      "zh": "我也可以看看那邊的鞋子嗎？",
      "ja": "あそこの靴も見せてください。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Which color?",
      "zh": "哪個顏色？",
      "ja": "どの色ですか？",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The white ones, please.",
      "zh": "白色的，謝謝。",
      "ja": "白いのをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "In size 7 and a half?",
      "zh": "7號半的嗎？",
      "ja": "7とハーフのサイズですか？",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait a moment, please.",
      "zh": "請稍等。",
      "ja": "少々お待ちください。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like both pairs.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這兩雙。",
      "ja": "両方とも気に入りました。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will take these.",
      "zh": "我要買這雙。",
      "ja": "これを買います。",
      "time": "00:04:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have you been here before?",
      "zh": "你以前來過這裡嗎？",
      "ja": "ここに来たことはありますか？",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "沒有。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is my first time.",
      "zh": "這是我第一次。",
      "ja": "初めてです。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can I have your phone number?",
      "zh": "可以給我你的電話號碼嗎？",
      "ja": "電話番号を教えていただけますか？",
      "time": "00:04:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is 615.",
      "zh": "是615。",
      "ja": "615です。",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And your name?",
      "zh": "你的名字是？",
      "ja": "お名前は？",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maya.",
      "zh": "瑪雅。",
      "ja": "マヤです。",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "M-A-Y-A.",
      "zh": "M-A-Y-A。",
      "ja": "M-A-Y-Aです。",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The total is $220.",
      "zh": "總共是220美元。",
      "ja": "合計は220ドルです。",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can use Apple Pay here.",
      "zh": "你可以用Apple Pay付款。",
      "ja": "ここではApple Payが使えます。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:05:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Done.",
      "zh": "完成了。",
      "ja": "支払い完了です。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a great day.",
      "zh": "祝你有美好的一天。",
      "ja": "良い一日を。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You too.",
      "zh": "你也是。",
      "ja": "あなたもね。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Bye.",
      "zh": "再見。",
      "ja": "さようなら。",
      "time": "00:05:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The city center is very busy.",
      "zh": "市中心非常熱鬧。",
      "ja": "市の中心はとても賑やかです。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like this place.",
      "zh": "我喜歡這個地方。",
      "ja": "この場所が好きです。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now it is 645.",
      "zh": "現在是6:45。",
      "ja": "今は6時45分です。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time for dinner.",
      "zh": "晚餐時間到了。",
      "ja": "夕食の時間です。",
      "time": "00:05:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The golden steakhouse is right over there.",
      "zh": "黃金牛排館就在那邊。",
      "ja": "ゴールデンステーキハウスはあそこです。",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "zh": "我們走吧。",
      "ja": "行きましょう。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi.",
      "zh": "嗨。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Welcome.",
      "zh": "歡迎光臨。",
      "ja": "いらっしゃいませ。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want some food first?",
      "zh": "你想先吃點東西嗎？",
      "ja": "先に何か食べますか？",
      "time": "00:05:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "すみません。",
      "time": "00:05:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What is that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "それは何ですか？",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is a small dish.",
      "zh": "那是一道小菜。",
      "ja": "それは小さな料理です。",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You eat it before your big meal.",
      "zh": "你在主餐前吃它。",
      "ja": "メインの食事の前に食べます。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I see.",
      "zh": "我懂了。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want the bread with tomato.",
      "zh": "我要番茄麵包。",
      "ja": "トマトのパンをください。",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The toasted bread with tomato?",
      "zh": "是烤過的番茄麵包嗎？",
      "ja": "トマトのトーストですか？",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That one.",
      "zh": "就是那個。",
      "ja": "それです。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Today we have steak with garlic sauce.",
      "zh": "今天有蒜味醬牛排。",
      "ja": "今日はガーリックソースのステーキがあります。",
      "time": "00:05:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want that?",
      "zh": "你要那個嗎？",
      "ja": "それにしますか？",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That sounds good.",
      "zh": "聽起來不錯。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:05:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do you want your steak?",
      "zh": "你的牛排要幾分熟？",
      "ja": "ステーキの焼き加減はどうしますか？",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A little red.",
      "zh": "稍微帶點紅。",
      "ja": "少し赤い感じで。",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A little pink or no red.",
      "zh": "稍微粉紅或不帶紅色。",
      "ja": "少しピンクか赤みなしで。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not too red.",
      "zh": "不要太紅。",
      "ja": "あまり赤くない方がいい。",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not too dry.",
      "zh": "不要太乾。",
      "ja": "あまり乾燥していない方がいい。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Medium.",
      "zh": "五分熟。",
      "ja": "ミディアムですね。",
      "time": "00:06:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want soup or salad?",
      "zh": "你要湯還是沙拉？",
      "ja": "スープかサラダはいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tomato soup.",
      "zh": "番茄湯。",
      "ja": "トマトスープを。",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anything to drink?",
      "zh": "要喝什麼嗎？",
      "ja": "飲み物はどうしますか？",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Water please.",
      "zh": "請給我水。",
      "ja": "お水をください。",
      "time": "00:06:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want dessert later?",
      "zh": "你要不要甜點？",
      "ja": "後でデザートはいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不要。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:06:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am full already.",
      "zh": "我已經飽了。",
      "ja": "もうお腹いっぱいです。",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your food will come soon.",
      "zh": "你的餐點很快就來。",
      "ja": "すぐに料理が届きます。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That was a great meal.",
      "zh": "那頓飯真好吃。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい食事でした。",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I am driving my rental car back to the hotel.",
      "zh": "現在我開租來的車回飯店。",
      "ja": "今、レンタカーでホテルに戻っています。",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:06:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What are those lights?",
      "zh": "那些燈是什麼？",
      "ja": "あのライトは何？",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no.",
      "zh": "喔不。",
      "ja": "やばい。",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not again.",
      "zh": "又來了。",
      "ja": "またか。",
      "time": "00:06:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:06:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you know why I stopped you?",
      "zh": "你知道我為什麼攔下你嗎？",
      "ja": "なぜ止めたかわかりますか？",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, officer.",
      "zh": "不知道，警官。",
      "ja": "いいえ、警官。",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is something wrong?",
      "zh": "有什麼問題嗎？",
      "ja": "何か問題ですか？",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your car moved left and right.",
      "zh": "你的車左右搖晃。",
      "ja": "車が左右に動いていました。",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Did you drink alcohol tonight?",
      "zh": "你今晚有喝酒嗎？",
      "ja": "今夜お酒を飲みましたか？",
      "time": "00:06:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, sir.",
      "zh": "沒有，先生。",
      "ja": "いいえ、飲んでいません。",
      "time": "00:06:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I did not drink.",
      "zh": "我沒喝酒。",
      "ja": "飲んでいません。",
      "time": "00:06:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The road is not smooth.",
      "zh": "路面不平。",
      "ja": "道路がでこぼこしているからかも。",
      "time": "00:06:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe that is why.",
      "zh": "可能是這個原因。",
      "ja": "それが原因かもしれません。",
      "time": "00:06:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:07:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please show me your ID.",
      "zh": "請出示你的身分證。",
      "ja": "身分証を見せてください。",
      "time": "00:07:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please get out of the car.",
      "zh": "請下車。",
      "ja": "車から降りてください。",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I will check if you are okay to drive.",
      "zh": "我要檢查你是否適合開車。",
      "ja": "運転できるか確認します。",
      "time": "00:07:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "First, say the ABC.",
      "zh": "先說ABC。",
      "ja": "まず、ABCを言ってください。",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A, B, C, D, E, F.",
      "zh": "A、B、C、D、E、F。",
      "ja": "エー、ビー、シー、ディー、イー、エフ。",
      "time": "00:07:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:07:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now look at my pen.",
      "zh": "現在看著我的筆。",
      "ja": "今、私のペンを見てください。",
      "time": "00:07:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not move your head.",
      "zh": "不要動頭。",
      "ja": "頭は動かさないで。",
      "time": "00:07:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Only move your eyes.",
      "zh": "只動眼睛。",
      "ja": "目だけ動かしてください。",
      "time": "00:07:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now walk in a straight line.",
      "zh": "現在直線走。",
      "ja": "まっすぐ歩いてください。",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Take nine steps.",
      "zh": "走九步。",
      "ja": "9歩歩いてください。",
      "time": "00:07:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Count your steps.",
      "zh": "數你的步數。",
      "ja": "歩数を数えて。",
      "time": "00:07:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One, two, three, eight, nine.",
      "zh": "一、二、三、八、九。",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん、はち、きゅう。",
      "time": "00:07:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now stand on one foot.",
      "zh": "現在單腳站立。",
      "ja": "今、片足で立ってください。",
      "time": "00:07:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Count slowly.",
      "zh": "慢慢數數。",
      "ja": "ゆっくり数えて。",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One, two, three.",
      "zh": "一、二、三。",
      "ja": "いち、に、さん。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好的。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:07:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Everything is fine.",
      "zh": "一切正常。",
      "ja": "問題ありません。",
      "time": "00:07:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You can drive.",
      "zh": "你可以開車了。",
      "ja": "運転しても大丈夫です。",
      "time": "00:07:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Drive safely.",
      "zh": "開車小心。",
      "ja": "安全運転で。",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, officer.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，警官。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます、警官。",
      "time": "00:08:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Everything is okay.",
      "zh": "一切都好。",
      "ja": "すべて問題ありません。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am a safe driver.",
      "zh": "我是一個安全的駕駛。",
      "ja": "私は安全なドライバーです。",
      "time": "00:08:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I am back at the hotel.",
      "zh": "現在我回到飯店了。",
      "ja": "今、ホテルに戻りました。",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is very late.",
      "zh": "已經很晚了。",
      "ja": "とても遅い時間です。",
      "time": "00:08:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just want to open my door and sleep.",
      "zh": "我只想開門睡覺。",
      "ja": "ただドアを開けて寝たい。",
      "time": "00:08:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:08:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where is my card?",
      "zh": "我的卡在哪裡？",
      "ja": "カードはどこ？",
      "time": "00:08:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good evening.",
      "zh": "晚上好。",
      "ja": "こんばんは。",
      "time": "00:08:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How can I help you?",
      "zh": "我能幫你什麼？",
      "ja": "どうされましたか？",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "你好。",
      "ja": "こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:08:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have a problem.",
      "zh": "我有問題。",
      "ja": "問題があります。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My key card is in my room.",
      "zh": "我的房卡在房間裡。",
      "ja": "部屋にキーが置きっぱなしです。",
      "time": "00:08:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, you cannot open your door?",
      "zh": "喔，你打不開門嗎？",
      "ja": "ああ、ドアが開かないのですか？",
      "time": "00:08:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:08:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The card is inside.",
      "zh": "卡在裡面。",
      "ja": "カードは中にあります。",
      "time": "00:08:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am outside.",
      "zh": "我在外面。",
      "ja": "私は外にいます。",
      "time": "00:08:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Very bad.",
      "zh": "很糟糕。",
      "ja": "それは困りましたね。",
      "time": "00:08:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫ですよ。",
      "time": "00:08:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is your room number?",
      "zh": "你的房號是多少？",
      "ja": "お部屋番号は？",
      "time": "00:08:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "ちょっと待って。",
      "time": "00:08:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I forget.",
      "zh": "我忘了。",
      "ja": "忘れました。",
      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe 618 or 681?",
      "zh": "可能是618或681？",
      "ja": "618か681かも？",
      "time": "00:08:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫です。",
      "time": "00:08:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "May I see your ID?",
      "zh": "可以看你的身分證嗎？",
      "ja": "身分証を見せてください。",
      "time": "00:08:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "zh": "好的，當然。",
      "ja": "はい、もちろんです。",
      "time": "00:08:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here.",
      "zh": "給你。",
      "ja": "どうぞ。",
      "time": "00:08:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you, Miss Maya.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，瑪雅小姐。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます、マヤさん。",
      "time": "00:08:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are in room 618.",
      "zh": "你住在618號房。",
      "ja": "お部屋は618号室です。",
      "time": "00:08:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I will make a new card.",
      "zh": "我會幫你做一張新卡。",
      "ja": "新しいカードを作りますね。",
      "time": "00:09:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:09:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:09:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You saved me.",
      "zh": "你救了我。",
      "ja": "助かりました。",
      "time": "00:09:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I almost sleep in the hallway.",
      "zh": "我差點睡在走廊。",
      "ja": "廊下で寝るところでした。",
      "time": "00:09:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like a sad cat.",
      "zh": "像隻悲傷的貓。",
      "ja": "悲しい猫みたいに。",
      "time": "00:09:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "そうですね。",
      "time": "00:09:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here is your new card.",
      "zh": "這是你的新卡。",
      "ja": "こちらが新しいカードです。",
      "time": "00:09:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:09:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The old card in the room.",
      "zh": "房間裡的舊卡。",
      "ja": "部屋の古いカードは。",
      "time": "00:09:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is it still okay?",
      "zh": "還可以用嗎？",
      "ja": "まだ使えますか？",
      "time": "00:09:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, it will not work now.",
      "zh": "不，現在不能用了。",
      "ja": "いいえ、もう使えません。",
      "time": "00:09:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a good day.",
      "zh": "祝你有美好的一天。",
      "ja": "良い一日を。",
      "time": "00:09:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:09:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You too.",
      "zh": "你也是。",
      "ja": "あなたもね。",
      "time": "00:09:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I have my new key.",
      "zh": "現在我有新房卡了。",
      "ja": "これで新しいキーがあります。",
      "time": "00:09:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Traveling alone is not easy.",
      "zh": "一個人旅行不容易。",
      "ja": "一人旅は簡単ではありません。",
      "time": "00:09:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But it is fun.",
      "zh": "但很有趣。",
      "ja": "でも楽しいです。",
      "time": "00:09:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Today was a long day.",
      "zh": "今天很長的一天。",
      "ja": "今日は長い一日でした。",
      "time": "00:09:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am very tired.",
      "zh": "我很累。",
      "ja": "とても疲れました。",
      "time": "00:09:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Time to sleep.",
      "zh": "該睡覺了。",
      "ja": "寝る時間です。",
      "time": "00:09:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night.",
      "zh": "晚安。",
      "ja": "おやすみなさい。",
      "time": "00:09:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "See you on day 3.",
      "zh": "第三天見。",
      "ja": "3日目にまた会いましょう。",
      "time": "00:09:44"
    }
  ]
}